4
00:00:14,920 --> 00:00:15,920
Miss Liao

5
00:00:15,920 --> 00:00:17,130
Come

6
00:00:17,130 --> 00:00:18,420
Let's have a drink first

7
00:00:23,670 --> 00:00:25,380
Such firm chest...

8
00:00:28,710 --> 00:00:30,420
Miss Liao

9
00:00:30,420 --> 00:00:33,130
let me explain first—

10
00:00:33,130 --> 00:00:35,420
The contract I signed with the club

11
00:00:35,420 --> 00:00:37,790
