12
00:00:37,790 --> 00:00:40,920
So if you're looking for other services,

13
00:00:40,920 --> 00:00:43,040
I can find you another host.

14
00:00:43,040 --> 00:00:44,920
Oh, come on

15
00:00:44,920 --> 00:00:48,670
You're my type of guy

16
00:00:48,670 --> 00:00:51,790
Why not reconsider?

17
00:00:51,790 --> 00:00:55,000
I can tip you extra.

18
00:00:56,710 --> 00:00:58,130
It's not about the money.

19
00:00:58,130 --> 00:01:00,170
Ow, that hurts!

20
00:01:00,170 --> 00:01:03,170
Ow… that hurts…

21
00:01:03,170 --> 00:01:04,629
That really hurts!

22
00:01:09,250 --> 00:01:12,170
Sorry, I'll drink as a penalty.

23
00:01:12,170 --> 00:01:14,750
Ouch, that really hurts.

24
00:01:14,750 --> 00:01:17,920
But it actually feels good.

25
00:01:18,789 --> 00:01:22,420
So you like playing rough?

26
00:01:22,420 --> 00:01:25,039
What a coincidence, I like it too.

27
00:01:25,039 --> 00:01:26,170
No, Miss Liao—

28
00:01:26,170 --> 00:01:28,289
Waiter, champagne!

29
00:01:28,289 --> 00:01:28,830
Miss Liao, let me explain—

30
00:01:28,830 --> 00:01:29,630
Come on

31
00:01:29,630 --> 00:01:30,630
Miss Liao—

32
00:01:32,210 --> 00:01:33,920
Cheers, everyone

33
00:01:40,630 --> 00:01:42,250
It's been a while…

34
00:01:46,289 --> 00:01:47,630
I'll come back for you later.

35
00:01:47,630 --> 00:01:48,750
Okay.

36
00:01:49,420 --> 00:01:50,880
Hey...

37
00:01:50,880 --> 00:01:52,789
Cheers… Thanks for coming

38
00:01:56,289 --> 00:01:57,420
Just have a little,

39
00:01:57,420 --> 00:01:59,830
