40
00:02:00,500 --> 00:02:02,880
I'm not much of a drinker.

41
00:02:02,880 --> 00:02:04,420
Then I'll get you some orange juice.

42
00:02:05,130 --> 00:02:06,250
Thank you

43
00:02:10,789 --> 00:02:12,040
Orange juice, please.

44
00:02:37,170 --> 00:02:38,540
Here you go

45
00:02:39,500 --> 00:02:40,630
Thanks

46
00:02:44,170 --> 00:02:46,670
Let's go, keep me company

47
00:02:50,250 --> 00:02:51,250
Hey

48
00:02:51,250 --> 00:02:52,329
Hi

49
00:02:52,329 --> 00:02:53,790
Cheers

50
00:02:53,790 --> 00:02:55,130
Hi

51
00:02:56,250 --> 00:02:57,500
Have some more, let's chat later

52
00:02:58,380 --> 00:03:00,000
Wei

53
00:03:00,000 --> 00:03:01,290
Jessica

54
00:03:01,290 --> 00:03:02,630
Come over and sit

55
00:03:05,170 --> 00:03:07,420
Your parties keep getting better and better.

56
00:03:07,420 --> 00:03:08,960
So your style…

57
00:03:08,960 --> 00:03:10,000
Thank you

58
00:03:12,750 --> 00:03:14,250
And this is…

59
00:03:14,250 --> 00:03:17,790
Daniel, a host here at the club. Nice to meet you.

60
00:03:18,960 --> 00:03:20,130
Daniel

61
00:03:27,420 --> 00:03:29,460
Daniel, come

62
00:03:30,040 --> 00:03:31,040
Sit

63
00:03:39,960 --> 00:03:41,000
Have fun

64
00:03:41,000 --> 00:03:42,250
Okay, thanks.

65
00:03:47,460 --> 00:03:49,960
