66
00:03:49,960 --> 00:03:51,130
No

67
00:03:51,130 --> 00:03:54,130
It's okay, relax.

68
00:03:54,130 --> 00:03:56,290
Here, wanna smoke?

69
00:03:56,290 --> 00:03:57,380
No, thanks

70
00:03:59,000 --> 00:04:00,420
Have some fruit

71
00:04:01,540 --> 00:04:02,540
Here

72
00:04:04,630 --> 00:04:05,790
No, thanks

73
00:04:07,290 --> 00:04:08,460
Shh…

74
00:04:09,380 --> 00:04:11,670
It's okay.

75
00:04:11,670 --> 00:04:13,500
You look hot…

76
00:04:13,500 --> 00:04:15,420
Let me take off your jacket.

77
00:04:15,420 --> 00:04:17,290
Take a deep breath.

78
00:04:18,540 --> 00:04:20,040
Relax

79
00:04:22,040 --> 00:04:23,920
It's okay

80
00:04:23,920 --> 00:04:24,920
I'll give you a massage

81
00:04:24,920 --> 00:04:25,920
Where are you going?

82
00:04:27,040 --> 00:04:28,130
Where are you going?

83
00:04:28,130 --> 00:04:29,790
Do you want to lie down?

84
00:04:34,000 --> 00:04:35,000
You should lie down.

85
00:04:35,000 --> 00:04:36,790
Come on

86
00:04:36,790 --> 00:04:37,920
