87
00:04:39,580 --> 00:04:41,040
Go get Tony

88
00:04:42,500 --> 00:04:44,710
It's okay.

89
00:04:44,710 --> 00:04:45,380
Excuse me

90
00:04:45,380 --> 00:04:47,540
It's fine, go do something else.

91
00:04:50,460 --> 00:04:51,920
I'll give you a massage.

92
00:04:58,790 --> 00:05:01,170
Breathe.

93
00:05:01,170 --> 00:05:03,670
Relax, take a deep breath.

94
00:05:03,670 --> 00:05:05,500
I'll help you relax.

95
00:05:23,500 --> 00:05:24,630
It's okay.

96
00:05:31,040 --> 00:05:32,500
Is your belt too tight?

97
00:05:40,000 --> 00:05:41,290
It's okay.

98
00:05:43,750 --> 00:05:44,920
Youth is wonderful

99
00:05:46,170 --> 00:05:47,790
Give me your hands

100
00:05:50,210 --> 00:05:51,790
Leave it to me.

101
00:05:54,880 --> 00:05:56,170
Don't be nervous.

102
00:05:57,750 --> 00:05:59,290
Relax

103
00:06:55,170 --> 00:06:59,040
Tony

104
00:07:00,210 --> 00:07:02,380
I didn't get picked

105
00:07:02,380 --> 00:07:04,670
and the main hall got booked

106
00:07:05,880 --> 00:07:08,040
A hero with nowhere to shine,

107
00:07:10,420 --> 00:07:14,830
can I go practice with Rou-rou?

108
00:07:15,630 --> 00:07:17,330
Practice what?

109
00:07:17,330 --> 00:07:19,750
Aren't you leaving at the end of the month?

110
00:07:19,750 --> 00:07:20,540
Once you're gone

111
00:07:20,540 --> 00:07:22,540
then you'll really have nowhere to shine.

112
00:07:22,540 --> 00:07:25,000
Come on, please.

113
00:07:25,750 --> 00:07:27,380
Alright, go.

114
00:07:27,380 --> 00:07:29,170
Stop annoying me.

115
00:07:29,170 --> 00:07:30,790
Tony, you're the best!

116
00:07:30,790 --> 00:07:32,420
I  love you

117
00:07:33,040 --> 00:07:36,130
Good thing I didn't return the car key this morning.

118
00:07:36,130 --> 00:07:38,250
Rou-rou baby, I'm coming!

119
00:07:58,000 --> 00:07:59,040
Excuse me

120
00:08:04,880 --> 00:08:06,960
Another one passed out drunk.

121
00:08:06,960 --> 00:08:08,330
Tony, something's wrong!

122
00:08:08,330 --> 00:08:09,580
Just now in the main hall

123
00:08:09,580 --> 00:08:11,420
Lee Xun was forced down on the couch

124
00:08:11,420 --> 00:08:12,750
and they even started unbuttoning his shirt.

125
00:08:17,880 --> 00:08:19,670
He completely lost it?

126
00:08:20,670 --> 00:08:22,380
Go notify Ma

127
00:08:22,380 --> 00:08:23,750
I'll go first in case things get worse.

128
00:08:23,750 --> 00:08:24,750
Okay

129
00:08:25,710 --> 00:08:27,040
What the hell happened?

130
00:08:28,290 --> 00:08:29,250
Asa

131
00:08:45,670 --> 00:08:47,540
What are you doing?!

132
00:08:47,540 --> 00:08:48,670
Stop it right now!

133
00:08:51,290 --> 00:08:52,420
Watch out!

134
00:09:10,500 --> 00:09:11,460
Yuchuan!

135
00:09:11,460 --> 00:09:13,040
Call an ambulance!

136
00:09:13,040 --> 00:09:14,330
Yuchuan!

137
00:09:14,330 --> 00:09:15,960
Hurry up

138
00:09:15,960 --> 00:09:17,750
Yuchuan!

139
00:09:17,750 --> 00:09:18,790
Hurry

140
00:09:24,040 --> 00:09:25,420
Didn't expect safes these days

141
00:09:25,420 --> 00:09:27,630
to be made this elegantly.

142
00:09:27,630 --> 00:09:28,290
I wouldn't even know it's a safe

143
00:09:28,290 --> 00:09:31,170
if you hadn't told me

144
00:09:35,000 --> 00:09:37,080
Looks like our diamond babies

145
00:09:37,080 --> 00:09:40,170
can rest comfortably inside

146
00:09:40,170 --> 00:09:43,290
and we can relax too.

147
00:09:46,040 --> 00:09:50,210
We don't have to worry anymore.

148
00:09:52,710 --> 00:09:54,670
You're so clever.

149
00:09:55,670 --> 00:09:57,540
Of course.

150
00:09:59,670 --> 00:10:03,130
Hey, do you remember last time at the club

151
00:10:03,130 --> 00:10:05,630
that handsome guy who picked me,the handsome guy?

152
00:10:05,630 --> 00:10:08,500
His name is David who is a director.

153
00:10:09,460 --> 00:10:12,290
He wants me to go to Thailand to film a BL series.

154
00:10:12,290 --> 00:10:13,580
I want to take you with me.

155
00:10:13,580 --> 00:10:17,250
Is he certain you’ve got what it takes to act?

156
00:10:18,080 --> 00:10:20,040
I'm not quite sure either

157
00:10:20,040 --> 00:10:22,750
But since someone believes in me that much,

158
00:10:22,750 --> 00:10:24,040
for our diamond babies

159
00:10:24,040 --> 00:10:25,960
and our future,

160
00:10:25,960 --> 00:10:27,750
I think it's worth giving it a shot.

161
00:10:32,540 --> 00:10:36,250
Does he know about the diamonds?

162
00:10:36,250 --> 00:10:38,670
Of course not.

163
00:10:39,460 --> 00:10:41,130
That's good then

164
00:10:41,130 --> 00:10:44,040
At least he’s not trying to trick you out of the diamonds

165
00:10:44,040 --> 00:10:45,790
by asking you to act.

166
00:10:48,790 --> 00:10:49,960
I doubt it.

167
00:10:49,960 --> 00:10:52,830
David seems pretty sincere to me

168
00:10:52,830 --> 00:10:54,670
The way he looks at me…

169
00:10:55,880 --> 00:10:57,290
it's full of love.

170
00:10:59,880 --> 00:11:02,670
Then maybe I should keep a closer eye on you

171
00:11:02,670 --> 00:11:06,670
so you don’t get swayed by his “love.”

172
00:11:06,670 --> 00:11:07,790
Don't worry

173
00:11:07,790 --> 00:11:11,460
I'm a straight guy through and through.

174
00:11:11,460 --> 00:11:12,500
Besides,

175
00:11:14,880 --> 00:11:18,170
You're the only one I love

176
00:11:23,790 --> 00:11:24,540
What are you up to?

177
00:11:32,380 --> 00:11:35,330
Andy, what happened?

178
00:11:35,330 --> 00:11:36,420
I just walked out of the VIP room,

179
00:11:36,420 --> 00:11:38,420
the main hall looked like hell broke loose.

180
00:11:38,420 --> 00:11:39,790
Among tonight’s guests,

181
00:11:39,790 --> 00:11:41,880
someone had bad intentions toward Lee Xun.

182
00:11:43,380 --> 00:11:46,670
Looks like he's drugged.

183
00:11:49,670 --> 00:11:51,830
What kind of trash does that?

184
00:11:51,830 --> 00:11:54,460
Drugging someone just because they couldn’t get him.

185
00:11:56,920 --> 00:11:58,420
No wonder Yuchuan went crazy.

186
00:12:00,460 --> 00:12:03,250
By the way, how’s Yuchuan?

187
00:12:03,250 --> 00:12:04,670
Is he hurt badly?

188
00:12:04,670 --> 00:12:06,380
I'm not sure

189
00:12:06,380 --> 00:12:09,290
But Tony and Ma took him to the hospital themselves.

190
00:12:09,290 --> 00:12:10,540
He should be okay.

191
00:12:13,790 --> 00:12:15,630
Thanks for taking care of Lee Xun.

192
00:12:15,630 --> 00:12:18,040
I'll go help clean up the main hall now.

193
00:12:18,040 --> 00:12:19,880
Alright, leave it to me here.

194
00:12:19,880 --> 00:12:21,080
Go ahead.

195
00:12:49,750 --> 00:12:52,170
Careful. Watch your step.

196
00:12:54,290 --> 00:12:55,420
Yuchuan.

197
00:12:57,040 --> 00:12:58,750
Sit down first.

198
00:13:01,750 --> 00:13:03,210
Are you okay?

199
00:13:03,210 --> 00:13:04,420
You're badly hurt.

200
00:13:09,540 --> 00:13:12,420
Yuchuan, get some rest.

201
00:13:14,710 --> 00:13:15,880
Let's step outside.

202
00:13:15,880 --> 00:13:17,170
Let them talk.

203
00:13:34,290 --> 00:13:36,420
Why were you so reckless?

204
00:13:36,420 --> 00:13:38,420
What if something had happened?

205
00:13:39,670 --> 00:13:41,750
You're a grown up man

206
00:13:41,750 --> 00:13:44,290
Why don't you know how to protect yourself?

207
00:13:44,290 --> 00:13:46,540
Don't drink anything given by others,

208
00:13:47,250 --> 00:13:49,380
Even a three-year-old knows that.

209
00:13:49,380 --> 00:13:51,130
How could you be so careless?

210
00:13:58,250 --> 00:14:00,630
If I had been a moment later…

211
00:14:01,630 --> 00:14:03,670
Do you know how bad it could've been?

212
00:14:05,250 --> 00:14:07,330
If something had happened to you

213
00:14:08,250 --> 00:14:09,790
I'd blame myself.

214
00:14:11,210 --> 00:14:13,170
How would I face your parents?

215
00:14:24,080 --> 00:14:28,170
If you just worried about explaining to my parents

216
00:14:29,460 --> 00:14:31,710
you didn’t have to risk yourself like that.

217
00:14:45,420 --> 00:14:49,920
You think I fought that hard

218
00:14:49,920 --> 00:14:52,380
just so I could explain to your parents?

219
00:14:57,130 --> 00:14:58,540
Isn't that so?

220
00:15:06,920 --> 00:15:09,920
Next time, don't be so reckless.

221
00:15:13,170 --> 00:15:14,380
You're all I have got

222
00:15:14,380 --> 00:15:16,580
I can't lose you.

223
00:15:22,040 --> 00:15:23,170
Don't be afraid.

224
00:15:24,330 --> 00:15:26,130
I'm here.

225
00:15:28,380 --> 00:15:30,130
I'll always be here.

226
00:15:48,460 --> 00:15:50,460
Don't worry.

227
00:15:50,460 --> 00:15:52,880
Lee Xun is with him.

228
00:15:52,880 --> 00:15:54,170
Let the two of them

229
00:15:54,170 --> 00:15:55,670
get some rest for the next couple days.

230
00:15:57,380 --> 00:15:59,500
I never expected

231
00:15:59,500 --> 00:16:02,380
Yuchuan would get hurt at my place.

232
00:16:06,630 --> 00:16:07,960
Don't blame yourself.

233
00:16:08,710 --> 00:16:10,710
You can't protect him forever.

234
00:16:11,330 --> 00:16:12,830
He's grown up.

235
00:16:12,830 --> 00:16:14,750
He needs to learn to rely on himself.

236
00:16:22,000 --> 00:16:23,420
By the way…

237
00:16:24,750 --> 00:16:26,630
Chao De-chiang called,

238
00:16:27,500 --> 00:16:30,920
he said Pan Hao stole his diamonds.

239
00:16:33,380 --> 00:16:35,040
Pan Hao?

240
00:16:36,710 --> 00:16:38,000
Does he look like someone

241
00:16:38,000 --> 00:16:40,000
who'd dare steal diamonds?

242
00:16:43,380 --> 00:16:45,130
Do you think

243
00:16:45,130 --> 00:16:47,000
I should help him handle Pan Hao?

244
00:16:47,920 --> 00:16:49,040
Of course not.

245
00:16:49,040 --> 00:16:50,500
How is that our problem?

246
00:16:50,500 --> 00:16:52,170
That's the ADS's business.

247
00:16:52,170 --> 00:16:53,920
They should handle it themselves.

248
00:16:55,420 --> 00:16:57,210
You should know their gan rules

249
00:16:57,210 --> 00:16:59,960
stop them from touching anyone from the club.

250
00:17:01,790 --> 00:17:03,710
Then it really isn't our problem.

251
00:17:03,710 --> 00:17:05,579
We didn't make their rules.

252
00:17:05,579 --> 00:17:07,500
Chao De-chiang can figure it out himself.

253
00:17:13,579 --> 00:17:14,880
Still...

254
00:17:14,880 --> 00:17:18,500
Yuchuan should probably know about this.

255
00:17:19,960 --> 00:17:21,710
After all, he brought Pan Hao here.

256
00:17:22,500 --> 00:17:24,829
If he doesn't know his background

257
00:17:24,829 --> 00:17:26,579
there could be more troubles later.

258
00:17:28,170 --> 00:17:29,920
Yuchuan,

259
00:17:29,920 --> 00:17:32,420
these guys you brought to the club

260
00:17:32,420 --> 00:17:35,130
do you really know their backgrounds?

261
00:17:35,130 --> 00:17:36,460
Well...

262
00:17:36,460 --> 00:17:39,040
I don't even fully know

263
00:17:39,040 --> 00:17:40,420
my own uncle's background.

264
00:17:50,170 --> 00:17:56,790
5 6 7 8 1 2 3 4

265
00:17:59,540 --> 00:18:05,170
2 2 3 4 5 6 7 8

266
00:18:05,170 --> 00:18:06,250
Boss Chiang, you wanted to see me?

267
00:18:06,250 --> 00:18:12,670
3 2 3 4 5 6 7 8

268
00:18:20,790 --> 00:18:22,040
What are you doing?

269
00:18:39,750 --> 00:18:42,130
I told you to deal with Lee Xun and Pan Hao.

270
00:18:42,130 --> 00:18:45,880
Not only did you fail

271
00:18:45,880 --> 00:18:48,040
you forced them to hide in the club.

272
00:18:51,080 --> 00:18:52,920
Ah-Biao…

273
00:18:52,920 --> 00:18:54,420
Now...

274
00:18:55,880 --> 00:18:57,540
how are you going to explain this?

275
00:19:03,790 --> 00:19:04,920
Talk

276
00:19:08,130 --> 00:19:11,170
Every single one of you is useless.

277
00:19:15,540 --> 00:19:16,210
Who was it

278
00:19:16,210 --> 00:19:19,000
making you angry so early?

279
00:19:23,420 --> 00:19:25,250
I'll be heartbroken

280
00:19:25,250 --> 00:19:27,210
if you ruin the health from anger

281
00:19:38,250 --> 00:19:39,380
Get out.

282
00:19:53,250 --> 00:19:55,040
Don't be mad.

283
00:19:55,040 --> 00:19:56,580
I made soup for you.

284
00:19:56,580 --> 00:19:58,540
Have some to nourish yourself.

285
00:20:03,130 --> 00:20:04,290
I'm fine

286
00:20:23,920 --> 00:20:24,880
Take a look

287
00:20:24,880 --> 00:20:26,420
Go ahead and sign it, if everything looks good,

288
00:20:26,420 --> 00:20:27,540
Okay

289
00:20:35,080 --> 00:20:36,460
Where’s your agent?

290
00:20:36,460 --> 00:20:38,170
Shouldn’t she be here to review this with you?

291
00:20:41,420 --> 00:20:43,170
She’s still at work.

292
00:20:48,540 --> 00:20:50,040
Hey...

293
00:20:51,130 --> 00:20:53,420
Do you really want to go to Thailand?

294
00:20:55,880 --> 00:20:58,920
So… when are we leaving?

295
00:21:00,920 --> 00:21:03,670
I’m flying to Thailand tomorrow for pre-production.

296
00:21:03,670 --> 00:21:04,920
I’ll bring you guys over for training

297
00:21:04,920 --> 00:21:06,670
around the middle of next month…

298
00:21:06,670 --> 00:21:08,920
We’ll start filming two months after that.

299
00:21:09,670 --> 00:21:11,670
So we have to wait until next month?

300
00:21:13,630 --> 00:21:15,170
Are you in a hurry?

301
00:21:15,170 --> 00:21:16,540
Did something happen?

302
00:21:16,540 --> 00:21:18,130
No, nothing.

303
00:21:24,630 --> 00:21:25,580
You suddenly changed your mind…

304
00:21:25,580 --> 00:21:27,630
Is it because of your girlfriend?

305
00:21:27,630 --> 00:21:29,920
If so, I should take her out for dinner

306
00:21:29,920 --> 00:21:31,540
to thank her properly

307
00:21:31,540 --> 00:21:32,880
Of course not.

308
00:21:32,880 --> 00:21:34,000
This is my own decision.

309
00:21:34,000 --> 00:21:35,670
Sorry, I need to take this call.

310
00:21:47,460 --> 00:21:49,170
Can I ask you a question?

311
00:21:49,170 --> 00:21:50,420
Why does David

312
00:21:50,420 --> 00:21:52,500
want me for this role so badly?

313
00:21:54,830 --> 00:21:57,040
You look a lot like his ex-boyfriend.

314
00:22:05,330 --> 00:22:08,210
Not just a little…

315
00:22:08,210 --> 00:22:10,170
We look identical

316
00:22:11,380 --> 00:22:14,920
Then why did they break up?

317
00:22:14,920 --> 00:22:17,040
They didn’t break up.

318
00:22:17,040 --> 00:22:20,250
His boyfriend had a car accident last year

319
00:22:20,250 --> 00:22:21,500
and passed away.

320
00:22:24,920 --> 00:22:27,630
They were supposed to go camping that day.

321
00:22:27,630 --> 00:22:30,750
But David got stuck with work.

322
00:22:30,750 --> 00:22:34,290
His boyfriend got upset and went alone,

323
00:22:34,290 --> 00:22:36,290
the accident happened on the way.

324
00:22:40,750 --> 00:22:41,670
The script

325
00:22:41,670 --> 00:22:44,500
was originally written for him.

326
00:22:45,460 --> 00:22:47,500
After the accident,

327
00:22:47,500 --> 00:22:49,750
the whole project stopped.

328
00:22:49,750 --> 00:22:53,000
So restarting it now…

329
00:22:53,000 --> 00:22:57,290
wouldn't that bring back his painful memories?

330
00:22:57,290 --> 00:22:59,630
He’s stronger than you think.

331
00:22:59,630 --> 00:23:01,040
Yes,

332
00:23:01,040 --> 00:23:03,500
you remind him of his boyfriend.

333
00:23:03,500 --> 00:23:08,710
But maybe this is also his way of saying goodbye.

334
00:23:16,920 --> 00:23:18,250
Everything okay?

335
00:23:18,250 --> 00:23:19,750
I’ve got another meeting shortly

336
00:23:21,130 --> 00:23:22,290
No problem.

337
00:23:26,080 --> 00:23:27,380
Looking forward to working together.

338
00:23:28,380 --> 00:23:29,750
Likewise.

339
00:23:34,790 --> 00:23:37,420
David, thank you.

340
00:23:39,250 --> 00:23:40,830
What’s this?

341
00:23:41,670 --> 00:23:43,290
Getting all sentimental now?

342
00:23:44,790 --> 00:23:48,130
Aren’t you flying to Thailand tomorrow?

343
00:23:48,130 --> 00:23:49,750
Safe travels.

344
00:23:49,750 --> 00:23:51,040
See you there.

345
00:23:53,920 --> 00:23:55,000
Alright,

346
00:23:55,790 --> 00:23:57,080
I’ll be waiting…

347
00:23:58,290 --> 00:23:59,500
See you in Thailand.

348
00:24:17,210 --> 00:24:20,750
An exclusive contract

349
00:24:20,750 --> 00:24:22,580
That scared the hell out of me.

350
00:24:23,380 --> 00:24:25,130
What's wrong with you?

351
00:24:26,250 --> 00:24:28,420
So... you finally decided to come back.

352
00:24:28,420 --> 00:24:29,290
No,

353
00:24:29,290 --> 00:24:31,420
I mean what happened to his head?

354
00:24:31,420 --> 00:24:32,710
Lee Xun got drugged

355
00:24:32,710 --> 00:24:35,080
at the party last night.

356
00:24:35,080 --> 00:24:36,920
Yu-chuan got there in time

357
00:24:36,920 --> 00:24:39,920
and knocked that creep out.

358
00:24:39,920 --> 00:24:41,540
But one of that creep's friends

359
00:24:41,540 --> 00:24:42,500
Clang!

360
00:24:42,500 --> 00:24:43,880
smashed a bottle

361
00:24:43,880 --> 00:24:45,290
over his head.

362
00:24:45,290 --> 00:24:47,000
That’s how he ended up like this.

363
00:24:47,000 --> 00:24:49,210
Luckily Tony and Ma

364
00:24:49,210 --> 00:24:51,000
got him to the hospital.

365
00:24:51,000 --> 00:24:52,290
Otherwise…

366
00:24:53,710 --> 00:24:55,460
Anyway, it's how he looks like this now

367
00:24:57,040 --> 00:24:58,380
I’m gone for just one night…

368
00:24:58,380 --> 00:25:02,330
and missed all the actions?

369
00:25:02,330 --> 00:25:03,540
Sounds like…

370
00:25:03,540 --> 00:25:04,420
you're disappointed you missed it

371
00:25:04,420 --> 00:25:05,630
on site

372
00:25:05,630 --> 00:25:07,670
or are you glad you didn’t get dragged into it?

373
00:25:07,670 --> 00:25:10,880
Hey… that’s not what I meant, Yuchuan

374
00:25:12,670 --> 00:25:15,290
But those guys from last night…

375
00:25:15,290 --> 00:25:19,130
they probably weren’t connected to ADS?

376
00:25:19,830 --> 00:25:20,790
I don’t think so.

377
00:25:20,790 --> 00:25:22,630
I didn’t see any of their Gang tattoos.

378
00:25:23,380 --> 00:25:24,960
I got something!

379
00:25:24,960 --> 00:25:27,170
Now we just need the key evidence from the accounts.

380
00:25:27,170 --> 00:25:28,580
Once we get that…

381
00:25:28,580 --> 00:25:30,670
We can report Chao De-chiang right away.

382
00:25:35,750 --> 00:25:38,000
Alright, when I go to Ah-Zhen's place next time…

383
00:25:38,000 --> 00:25:39,500
I’ll keep an eye out for you guys.

384
00:25:44,250 --> 00:25:47,170
If Chiang really goes down…

385
00:25:47,920 --> 00:25:50,420
Does that mean I won’t have to run anymore?

386
00:25:52,380 --> 00:25:53,790
Wait…

387
00:25:53,790 --> 00:25:55,630
Even if the ADS is gone…

388
00:25:55,630 --> 00:25:57,630
there’s still the F.T. Crew

389
00:25:59,630 --> 00:26:02,170
You said you just signed the contract?

390
00:26:02,170 --> 00:26:04,040
Oh right.

391
00:26:04,040 --> 00:26:07,290
I’m flying to Thailand to start training

392
00:26:07,290 --> 00:26:09,040
around the middle or end of next month.

393
00:26:10,250 --> 00:26:12,210
Speaking of which…

394
00:26:12,210 --> 00:26:13,380
Didn’t we catch that guy Ah-Jun …

395
00:26:13,380 --> 00:26:15,790
stealing your diamonds?

396
00:26:15,790 --> 00:26:18,000
He just disappeared.

397
00:26:18,000 --> 00:26:20,170
What happened to those diamonds?

398
00:26:20,170 --> 00:26:22,000
You should really be careful.

399
00:26:22,000 --> 00:26:25,290
You might end up losing both the girl and the money.

400
00:26:27,420 --> 00:26:28,540
Hey,

401
00:26:29,250 --> 00:26:31,040
money aside…

402
00:26:31,830 --> 00:26:34,290
Why would I lose the girl too?

403
00:26:35,790 --> 00:26:38,000
Bro...

404
00:26:38,000 --> 00:26:40,000
What girl

405
00:26:40,000 --> 00:26:42,250
would stay with her boyfriend who

406
00:26:42,250 --> 00:26:44,290
goes from billionaire to be broke overnight?

407
00:26:44,290 --> 00:26:45,500
Story like that

408
00:26:45,500 --> 00:26:48,540
only happens in novels.

409
00:26:48,540 --> 00:26:51,960
I believe Rourou would.

410
00:26:51,960 --> 00:26:54,330
That's okay

411
00:26:54,330 --> 00:26:57,830
You've still got David.

412
00:26:58,630 --> 00:27:00,130
That's right

413
00:27:00,130 --> 00:27:01,460
If Rourou leaves,

414
00:27:01,460 --> 00:27:03,670
I still have David.

415
00:27:04,920 --> 00:27:06,250
What nonsense are you talking about?

416
00:27:06,250 --> 00:27:07,130
I'm telling you

417
00:27:07,130 --> 00:27:08,210
Guys,

418
00:27:08,210 --> 00:27:10,500
are definitely not my thing.

419
00:27:11,250 --> 00:27:13,130
What’s wrong with guys?

420
00:27:14,040 --> 00:27:15,580
Why not?

421
00:27:27,580 --> 00:27:29,500
These are the profiles of our companions

422
00:27:35,580 --> 00:27:37,540
Judging from how she’s dressed…

423
00:27:37,540 --> 00:27:39,580
She’ll probably pick Jay or Justin.

424
00:27:39,580 --> 00:27:42,500
With that taste, I bet she’ll go for Jay, the bad-boy type.

425
00:27:46,580 --> 00:27:48,290
Welcome to A.C.E.

426
00:27:48,290 --> 00:27:50,750
May I introduce our hosts to you?

427
00:27:50,750 --> 00:27:52,080
This one.

428
00:27:53,000 --> 00:27:55,670
Sure,  I’ll arrange right away.

429
00:27:57,000 --> 00:27:58,250
Go inform Jay.

430
00:27:58,250 --> 00:27:59,750
Don’t keep the guest waiting.

431
00:27:59,750 --> 00:28:01,170
Got it.

432
00:28:09,500 --> 00:28:13,380
Without Yuchuan and Lee Xun…

433
00:28:13,380 --> 00:28:17,710
how many customers do I have to cover tonight?

434
00:28:18,420 --> 00:28:21,000
I’m already seeing double.

435
00:28:21,920 --> 00:28:23,630
Chenghan

436
00:28:24,330 --> 00:28:27,880
I miss you so much.

437
00:28:27,880 --> 00:28:29,790
Miss Hsu Chenghan?

438
00:28:29,790 --> 00:28:32,880
Want him to come scare your customers away?

439
00:28:32,880 --> 00:28:35,040
I’m going to die

440
00:28:35,040 --> 00:28:37,040
If I keep drinking

441
00:28:37,040 --> 00:28:38,210
I don't want to drink anymore

442
00:28:38,210 --> 00:28:40,250
How much did you drink?

443
00:28:42,580 --> 00:28:44,290
Just three bottles?

444
00:28:44,290 --> 00:28:47,540
Three bottles of whisky!

445
00:28:49,500 --> 00:28:51,170
And you’re still alive?

446
00:28:51,170 --> 00:28:52,380
Jay

447
00:28:52,380 --> 00:28:54,580
you’ve got a client.

448
00:28:54,580 --> 00:28:56,210
Again?

449
00:28:56,210 --> 00:29:00,540
Lily, are you trying to kill me?

450
00:29:00,540 --> 00:29:02,130
Tony said

451
00:29:02,130 --> 00:29:03,710
she’s a big spender.

452
00:29:03,710 --> 00:29:05,880
So hurry up.

453
00:29:05,880 --> 00:29:07,170
A rich client?

454
00:29:07,170 --> 00:29:09,630
Lucky you.

455
00:29:11,000 --> 00:29:12,170
Yihao

456
00:29:12,170 --> 00:29:13,960
We can go to Tony if you want this client

457
00:29:13,960 --> 00:29:15,500
Let's switch, okay?

458
00:29:15,500 --> 00:29:16,080
Please…

459
00:29:16,080 --> 00:29:16,920
nuh… you go ahead.

460
00:29:16,920 --> 00:29:17,790
I can't drink as much as you do

461
00:29:17,790 --> 00:29:19,670
You go

462
00:29:19,670 --> 00:29:20,250
Go make some money!

463
00:29:20,250 --> 00:29:21,880
Let's go

464
00:29:23,420 --> 00:29:25,250
Where did this old lady come from...

465
00:29:25,250 --> 00:29:28,130
roaming around this late disturbing people?

466
00:29:28,130 --> 00:29:31,630
Call Chenghan to rescue me.

467
00:29:31,630 --> 00:29:32,920
Sure, no problem.

468
00:29:32,920 --> 00:29:35,000
If you break the sales record tonight,

469
00:29:35,000 --> 00:29:37,170
I’ll pop champagne for you.

470
00:30:21,080 --> 00:30:22,880
What is it?

471
00:30:22,880 --> 00:30:24,670
I need you to catch someone

472
00:30:24,670 --> 00:30:26,130
alive.

473
00:30:27,580 --> 00:30:28,630
Alive?

474
00:30:29,380 --> 00:30:30,540
No can do.

475
00:30:31,790 --> 00:30:33,710
I’m not interested in live targets.

476
00:30:33,710 --> 00:30:34,750
Wait...

477
00:30:37,750 --> 00:30:40,080
I’ll pay a 500 deposit right now.

478
00:30:40,080 --> 00:30:43,540
the remaining 1,000 will be transferred once it’s done.

479
00:30:47,330 --> 00:30:48,580
Yu…

480
00:30:49,500 --> 00:30:50,880
Money doesn't matter,

481
00:30:51,670 --> 00:30:55,000
either 500 or 1000...

482
00:30:55,790 --> 00:30:59,750
The point is, I only take jobs that interest me.

483
00:31:00,750 --> 00:31:01,960
At that place…

484
00:31:03,420 --> 00:31:05,210
There’s someone you’ll be interested in.

485
00:31:08,750 --> 00:31:09,710
Who is it?

486
00:31:10,880 --> 00:31:11,920
The elder

487
00:31:23,080 --> 00:31:26,420
Hey, look—buy one get one free!

488
00:31:26,420 --> 00:31:27,460
What is it?

489
00:31:27,460 --> 00:31:28,630
Drinks

490
00:31:28,630 --> 00:31:30,080
You want one?

491
00:31:30,080 --> 00:31:31,830
I can’t drink that yet.

492
00:31:31,830 --> 00:31:32,920
Soon, though.

493
00:31:32,920 --> 00:31:34,250
I’ll get it for you once you’re discharged.

494
00:31:34,250 --> 00:31:35,920
Okay… but that’s still a long way to go

495
00:31:43,040 --> 00:31:44,880
Look at this.

496
00:31:44,880 --> 00:31:47,170
It looks so delicious

497
00:31:47,170 --> 00:31:48,670
Such a good deal too.

498
00:31:48,670 --> 00:31:50,130
Buy five, get two free.

499
00:31:50,130 --> 00:31:52,170
Why is there a "buy four get four free"?

500
00:31:52,170 --> 00:31:54,790
No idea… maybe because it’s Children’s Day.

501
00:32:10,380 --> 00:32:12,040
I went to the club looking for you several times

502
00:32:12,040 --> 00:32:13,420
but you were never there.

503
00:32:14,130 --> 00:32:16,040
I had to nag Tony for ages…

504
00:32:16,040 --> 00:32:18,130
before he finally told me you're here.

505
00:32:21,540 --> 00:32:23,540
Is something wrong for

506
00:32:24,170 --> 00:32:25,670
you to look for me so urgently?

507
00:32:37,210 --> 00:32:39,040
I really like you.

508
00:32:53,750 --> 00:32:58,630
You saw it yourself

509
00:32:58,630 --> 00:33:01,960
I have a sister who needs me,

510
00:33:01,960 --> 00:33:05,170
the only thing I can do is to make more money

511
00:33:05,170 --> 00:33:06,210
to cover her medical bills

512
00:33:06,210 --> 00:33:08,500
and to take care of her.

513
00:33:10,040 --> 00:33:11,290
I really..

514
00:33:11,290 --> 00:33:13,540
can't afford taking care of another person

515
00:33:17,170 --> 00:33:18,500
I'm sorry.

516
00:33:23,130 --> 00:33:25,880
Who said I wanted you to carry the burden?

517
00:33:25,880 --> 00:33:27,960
I really like you.

518
00:33:27,960 --> 00:33:30,830
I’m not asking you to take care of me.

519
00:33:32,420 --> 00:33:34,420
I ask for nothing

520
00:33:34,420 --> 00:33:36,670
If you’re willing…

521
00:33:36,670 --> 00:33:38,540
Shall we give it a try?

522
00:33:54,920 --> 00:33:56,790
What are you looking at now?

523
00:33:59,500 --> 00:34:01,710
Where’s that lady from earlier?

524
00:34:01,710 --> 00:34:03,040
Where did she go?

525
00:34:03,040 --> 00:34:05,130
She left. Why?

526
00:34:08,380 --> 00:34:12,170
I actually wanted to ask her to take you away.

527
00:34:13,170 --> 00:34:14,670
Why?

528
00:34:16,000 --> 00:34:17,920
Hsu Xiaoxi, I’ve treated you so well…

529
00:34:17,920 --> 00:34:19,630
and you want to push me away?

530
00:34:20,750 --> 00:34:22,080
No, that’s not it.

531
00:34:22,830 --> 00:34:25,380
It’s because you’re too good to me.

532
00:34:25,380 --> 00:34:27,670
I don’t want to keep being a burden to you.

533
00:34:34,750 --> 00:34:36,000
What are you talking about?

534
00:34:38,540 --> 00:34:40,580
You’re my sister

535
00:34:40,580 --> 00:34:42,540
and you’ve never been a burden to me.

536
00:34:45,420 --> 00:34:46,880
Hey,

537
00:34:47,750 --> 00:34:50,000
I already have a healthy heart.

538
00:34:50,000 --> 00:34:52,130
I’m recovering bit by bit.

539
00:34:52,130 --> 00:34:53,670
You don’t have to live your life

540
00:34:53,670 --> 00:34:56,040
around me anymore.

541
00:34:56,920 --> 00:34:58,880
So you can go pursue…

542
00:34:58,880 --> 00:35:00,290
your own happiness.

543
00:35:11,080 --> 00:35:15,790
What about that lady makes you think…

544
00:35:15,790 --> 00:35:18,540
that I'd be happy with her?

545
00:35:20,670 --> 00:35:23,380
The way she looks at you…

546
00:35:23,380 --> 00:35:27,170
I can tell she's really into you.

547
00:35:28,170 --> 00:35:29,790
How would you know?

548
00:35:31,920 --> 00:35:34,380
I just do

549
00:35:34,380 --> 00:35:36,250
I can feel it.

550
00:35:41,540 --> 00:35:45,170
With such a high fever and still say you’re fine.

551
00:35:45,170 --> 00:35:47,130
You must have been overloaded lately.

552
00:35:47,130 --> 00:35:48,750
Your body finally gave out.

553
00:35:50,080 --> 00:35:53,580
Here, take the med.

554
00:36:03,080 --> 00:36:04,500
I'm okay…

555
00:36:04,500 --> 00:36:05,880
just need some sleep.

556
00:36:08,040 --> 00:36:09,460
Then get some rest.

557
00:36:09,460 --> 00:36:12,250
Call me if you need anything.

558
00:37:29,420 --> 00:37:30,750
Zhen,

559
00:37:30,750 --> 00:37:33,380
make sure you eat properly while you’re sick.

560
00:37:33,380 --> 00:37:34,420
All the food on the table

561
00:37:34,420 --> 00:37:36,420
I prepared for you

562
00:37:36,420 --> 00:37:37,670
and the chicken soup in the pot

563
00:37:37,670 --> 00:37:39,380
that took me all afternoon….

564
00:37:39,380 --> 00:37:41,170
Make sure you finish it.

565
00:37:41,170 --> 00:37:43,040
I’m heading back to the club for work.

566
00:37:43,040 --> 00:37:44,830
Call me if you need anything.

567
00:37:44,830 --> 00:37:46,420
I'll come over right away

568
00:37:47,170 --> 00:37:48,460
And really—finish it.

569
00:38:33,170 --> 00:38:34,540
Thank you.

570
00:39:17,380 --> 00:39:18,420
Drink as much as you like. Have fun.

571
00:39:18,420 --> 00:39:20,000
Let me know if you need anything.

572
00:39:29,040 --> 00:39:30,040
Enjoy yourselves.

573
00:39:35,330 --> 00:39:37,250
Welcome to A.C.E.

574
00:39:38,500 --> 00:39:39,960
Is this your first time here?

575
00:39:39,960 --> 00:39:41,540
Would you like me to introduce our hosts?

576
00:39:46,460 --> 00:39:47,880
I want him.

577
00:39:47,880 --> 00:39:48,880
VIP room.

578
00:39:56,500 --> 00:39:58,130
I’ll arrange it right away.

579
00:39:58,130 --> 00:39:59,670
Lily

580
00:40:01,920 --> 00:40:03,380
Get Room A ready

581
00:40:04,330 --> 00:40:05,790
Right this way.

582
00:40:42,920 --> 00:40:44,040
Pan Hao.

583
00:40:46,540 --> 00:40:49,170
Ma? What are you doing here?

584
00:40:49,170 --> 00:40:51,500
The lady inside is a very important guest of mine.

585
00:40:51,500 --> 00:40:53,170
Since you’re the one serving her…

586
00:40:53,170 --> 00:40:56,880
you should give her the best.

587
00:40:58,540 --> 00:41:00,000
Go find Tony.

588
00:41:00,000 --> 00:41:03,670
Bring the best bottle in the house.

589
00:41:03,670 --> 00:41:04,330
Yes

590
00:41:04,330 --> 00:41:05,420
Go

591
00:41:17,790 --> 00:41:19,670
Shouldn’t you be entertaining your guest?

592
00:41:19,670 --> 00:41:21,420
Ma asked me to grab a bottle of wine

593
00:41:21,420 --> 00:41:24,790
He said the one who picked me is his VIP guest.

594
00:41:24,790 --> 00:41:26,290
VIP guest?

595
00:41:26,290 --> 00:41:27,290
He even told me to go to the wine cellar…

596
00:41:27,290 --> 00:41:29,170
and bring the best one for her.

597
00:41:42,380 --> 00:41:44,080
Miss,

598
00:41:44,080 --> 00:41:46,670
I suggest you don’t cause trouble in my place.

599
00:41:46,670 --> 00:41:47,540
Otherwise...

600
00:42:26,210 --> 00:42:28,040
It's really you

601
00:42:28,040 --> 00:42:29,250
The elder.

602
00:42:30,750 --> 00:42:32,540
I have no idea what you’re talking about.

603
00:42:32,540 --> 00:42:33,750
All these years…

604
00:42:33,750 --> 00:42:36,040
every piece of information I could find about you…

605
00:42:36,040 --> 00:42:37,750
I’ve studied it hundreds of times.

606
00:42:38,670 --> 00:42:40,920
No one’s ever captured your face on camera…

607
00:42:40,920 --> 00:42:42,540
But your fighting style…

608
00:42:42,540 --> 00:42:44,170
I’d recognize it anywhere.

609
00:42:45,630 --> 00:42:47,790
You’ve got the wrong person.

610
00:42:47,790 --> 00:42:49,710
I’ve been an assassin for five years…

611
00:42:49,710 --> 00:42:52,380
waiting for you to return.

612
00:42:52,380 --> 00:42:54,290
Today, I finally found you.

613
00:42:56,960 --> 00:42:58,790
Who sent you?

614
00:42:58,790 --> 00:43:00,500
What do you want?

615
00:43:01,630 --> 00:43:03,290
That’s not important.

616
00:43:03,290 --> 00:43:04,670
What matters is…

617
00:43:04,670 --> 00:43:06,290
Nothing in this world…

618
00:43:06,290 --> 00:43:08,960
is more thrilling than destroying someone

619
00:43:08,960 --> 00:43:10,920
you once worshiped in person.

620
00:43:12,420 --> 00:43:13,540
You think you can do that?

621
00:43:15,670 --> 00:43:17,210
Try and find out

